race.comment: SPARTUS (6) grows a leg for hoop Jones who has three wins from just four steers and will be high on confidence following that last-start victory over this track and trip. Looks the one they all have to run down. MY NAME IS (4) has a win and a second from two attempts over this course and distance and has tuned up for this with a recent trial victory. Include from the low draw. CAMPAI (2) has won two of his past four and gets some weight off with the 2kg claim. Hard to beat in this suitable contest. RUSSIAN MINT (1) is one from one around this circuit and may run a big race while fresh. The well-related ALL STASHED UP (8) (full to G3 winner and G2 placed Hidden Wealth) rounds out the selections.
